quran[14]{c,v,t,f}:
  55,61,"Then which of the Blessings of your Lord will you both (jinn and men) deny?"
  55,62,"And besides these two, there are two other Gardens (i.e. in Paradise)."
  55,63,"Then which of the Blessings of your Lord will you both (jinn and men) deny?"
